Question: Select customer emails and their total purchase amount by joining customers, purchases, and items, limited to the top 5 buyers.
Call: { "func_call": "select_with_join", "table": "customers", "columns": ["customers.email", "SUM(items.price * items.qty) as total_purchase"], "where": "customers.id = purchases.cust_id AND purchases.id = items.purchase_id", "limit": 5 }
Response: { "rows": [{"email": "james@webdev.com", "total_purchase": 22100.75}, {"email": "linda@artistry.org", "total_purchase": 18900.00}, {"email": "robert@cloudsys.net", "total_purchase": 14200.50}], "count": 3, "query_ms": 38 }
