Question: Retrieve book titles and library sections by joining books and shelves for items marked as 'fiction'.
Call: { "func_call": "select_with_join", "table": "books", "columns": ["books.title", "shelves.section_name"], "where": "books.shelf_id = shelves.id AND books.genre = 'fiction'", "limit": 30 }
Response: { "rows": [{"title": "The Silent Ocean", "section_name": "Row A"}, {"title": "Midnight Train", "section_name": "Row B"}, {"title": "Echoes of Time", "section_name": "Row A"}], "count": 3, "query_ms": 19 }
