Question: List artist names and album titles by joining artists and albums where the artist is from 'USA'.
Call: { "func_call": "select_with_join", "table": "artists", "columns": ["artists.name", "albums.title"], "where": "artists.id = albums.artist_id AND artists.country = 'USA'", "limit": 20 }
Response: { "rows": [{"name": "The Rockers", "title": "Night Drive"}, {"name": "Jazz Quartet", "title": "Blue Notes"}, {"name": "Pop Stars", "title": "Summer Hits"}], "count": 3, "query_ms": 16 }
